Class Profile

java.lang.Object
banking.Profile
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Profile>
public class Profile extends Object implements Comparable<Profile>
The Profile class holds the information regarding a person who holds the bank account, Full name and date of birth are part of their profile.

      public int compareTo(Profile other)

      Specified by:
      compareTo in interface Comparable<Profile>
      Parameters:

      Returns:
